So this is what I did. First I downloaded this torrent then I got a working copy of Alcohol120% off LimeWier then I opened up Alcohol120% and selected image burning wizard and opened up the folder that I had this torrent in then I had to select the show all files option at the bottom of the window to see the .bin files and then I just selected the diablo2cd1.bin file and only the diablo2cd1.bin file and started the burn using all the standard default settings and I did that for all 3 CDs and then install like a normal PC game. That?s it just remember that 

CD 1 is the install disk
CD 2 is the Play disc 
CD 3 is Cinematic disc
